articles.author: Helen Regan, Robert Shackelford
articles.title: Australia braces for more destruction as deadly floods devastate northeast - CNN
articles.description: Deadly floodwaters triggered by record rainfall in Australia’s northeast rose for a third day Monday as authorities warned flood-stricken communities to brace themselves for further destruction.
